t: Praise*pn the Lord!*s Praise*ln God in his sanctuary; praise*ld him in his mighty heavens!
Praise*ln him for his mighty deeds; praise*ld him according to his excellent greatness!
Praise*pn him with trumpet sound; praise*ld him with lute and harp!
Praise*ln him with tambourine and dance; praise*ld him with strings and pipe!
Praise*ln him with sounding cymbals; praise*ld him with loud clashing cymbals!
Let*ln everything that has breath praise the Lord!*s Praise*ln the Lord!*s
